Europe Trip during May 2007.

= Itinerary =

The plan is to visit Italy, France, then Spain. I fly to Rome. Once inside Europe, I take the train from city to city using a Eurail pass (cheaper than I expected). Then, eventually make my way to Spain

= Expenses =

Eurail Pass: $291

{{{
3 Countries 6 + 1 days in 2 months Promo  	2nd Class
}}}

Flight: $1028 
{{{
YVR > FCO (9am - 11am) 17h
MAD > YVR (6:20am - 4:28pm) 19h08m                
}}}
